The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Prof. Shetty meeting

New Delhi: Tournament director Prof. Ratnakar Shetty Thursday met home secretary V K Duggal here to discuss the security arrangements for the Champions Trophy beginning on Saturday 

Shetty asked for fool-proof security for all the ten teams taking part in the competition which would be held across four venues in the country. 

Duggal, on his part, assured that adequate security would be provided. 

 (PTI) 




